Localization.Name: ORC-mkX Arms Scorched
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Armor
Damage Reduction: 30%
Temp. Rating: -61 / 91 C
Radiation Protection: 26400 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s

The mark X is the latest in CDS’ award-winning Omni-Role Combat armor series. This EVA-rated suit features new EdgeCore composite weave technology, maximizing protection against projectiles, explosives and the elements while minimizing operator agility.

Localization.Name: Defiance Core Scorched
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Armor
Damage Reduction: 40%
Temp. Rating: -72 / 102 °C
Radiation Protection: 26800 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 8.0 µSCU
Backpacks: All

Incorporating the same manufacturing know-how and expertise that the UEE Marines have come to rely on, Clark Defense Systems has designed their civilian-line of Defiance heavy armors to stand firm in the face of even the most adverse combat scenarios with its three-star rated protective plating and fully integrated mobility framework.
